<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">المُشَاكَهَةُ:</span> المُشَابَهَةُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وقَوْلُهم <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: شَاكِهْ: أي قارِبْ-في المَدْح-وشابِهْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
